Interactive Data Map

Receiver array data were last downloaded August 2023. Our receivers have heard from all 56 tagged fish, and most recently heard from 30 tagged individuals. 37 fish have been detected by receivers placed outside of the preserve. 9 fish were last detected by receivers outside of the preserve. Click on a specific receiver in the map below to see the species the receiver has detected. Click each waterbody to show where tagged fish were initially caught and released.
